message:
Local server for tests

- Created custom-not-usable certs-keys for tests purposes
- Modified the code for create local server thread apart
- Modified tests for connect to local server, not to real Devo

Fixes in API and refactoring code of API and Sender v1.6.0 - 2019-01-09

Changed
 * Mild refactoring of Sender class
 * Refactoring API Response processing

Fixed
 * API responses blank lines and splitted lines
 * Problems with API CLI and automatic shutdowns

Changed
 * Typos in docs
Updated version in changelog and __version__ files
Modified version in changelog, readme and version files
Updated changelog, version and README version
Updated version file and README version
Modified processors, now we can process by default in yield with some defaults options
Added documentation and fixes configuration for python 2.7
Added flag revise to api query, for make insecure calls if client need it
Problems with recursion depth when zipped send has problems with Socket.
Changed all new endpoints references for sender and api
Fixed little bug with new confiuration init and update changelog-version
Fixed: Sender for logging (Handler) get Severity correctly
Fixed bug in  Sender CLI introduced in version 2.2.2
Changed Options to ClientConfig, and fix tests, code and READMES
Fixed dates in Client when int, and overriding tag in sender

[3.0.3] - 2019-09-25

Fixed
 * Fixed reconnection to socket in every send instruction of Sender
 * Code style changes
 * Added pep8speaks file for Github

Version 3.1.0

 - Modified logs to add level by handler, not by logger only
 - Updated/Fix documentation
 - Added read pfx certs in Sender

[3.1.1] - 2019-11-12

Added
 * Support to CA_MD_TOO_WEAK problems with a new flag "sec_level"
 * New flag documentation

Changed
 * SSL Socket in Sender creation with custom context
 * Tests Sender certificates generation/files are updated

Fixed
 * Problems in documentation with API information
Updated documentation, changelog, version and deleted prints for tests
Fixed bug introduced with last changes
change version in README.md flag url / devo/version.py
Added new security flags to Sender SSL Sender
Added new flags in sender CLI and new function for buffer options
Added examples and remove two typos/spaces
Fixed problem with row types in Lookup creation

docs: add Sender and API endpoints for Canada region

Additionally, both lists are converted to tables.
